---
import Layout from '../../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const title = "Antigua and Barbuda Citizenship by Investment Guide 2025";
const description = "Complete guide to Antigua and Barbuda's CBI program. $100,000 NDF donation option, 150+ countries visa-free, family-friendly pricing, and full insurance requirements for Caribbean citizenship.";

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": title,
  "description": description,
  "author": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Compare Expat Plans"
  },
  "datePublished": "2025-01-15",
  "dateModified": "2025-01-15"
};
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />

  <PageShell
    title={title}
    subtitle="Your complete guide to citizenship by investment in Antigua and Barbuda"
    heroImage="/images/countries/antigua-and-barbuda-hero-bg.png"
  >
    <!-- Quick Facts Box -->
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Antigua and Barbuda CBI: Quick Facts</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Minimum Investment:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> $100,000 NDF donation</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Processing Time:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> 3-6 months</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Visa-Free Countries:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> 150+ (including UK, EU, Hong Kong)</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Residency Requirement:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> 5 days in 5 years</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Family Inclusion:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> Spouse, children, parents, siblings</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Insurance Requirement:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> Required for application</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section id="overview" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Overview</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        Antigua and Barbuda's Citizenship by Investment Program, established in 2013, offers one of the Caribbean's
        most family-friendly paths to a second passport. With the lowest per-person costs for larger families (up to
        6 dependents for the same price as a couple), it's particularly attractive for families seeking visa-free
        access to 150+ countries including the UK, Schengen Area, Hong Kong, and Singapore.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        The program requires only 5 days of physical presence over 5 years to maintain citizenship—the most minimal
        residency requirement among Caribbean CBI programs. This makes it ideal for investors who want the benefits of
        Caribbean citizenship without committing to actual relocation. The twin-island nation also offers no income,
        capital gains, or inheritance tax for residents.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        Healthcare in Antigua is centered around Mount St. John's Medical Centre, the only public hospital. For serious
        medical issues, evacuation to Miami, Puerto Rico, or Barbados is standard. International health insurance with
        evacuation coverage is essential for anyone spending time on the islands.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Quick Decision Guide -->
    <section id="decision-guide" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Quick Decision Guide</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">Antigua CBI is Ideal If You:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-900">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Have a larger family (best value for 4-6 person families)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Want minimal physical presence requirements (5 days/5 years)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Need UK and EU visa-free access</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Want to include extended family (parents, grandparents, siblings)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Prefer an established program with consistent processing</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-3">Consider Alternatives If You:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-amber-900">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Are a single applicant (Dominica is cheaper for individuals)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Need US E-2 Treaty access (choose Grenada instead)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Want fastest processing (Vanuatu is 30-60 days)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Require excellent local healthcare (limited options)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Plan to actually relocate (consider St. Kitts for better infrastructure)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Official Requirements -->
    <section id="requirements" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Official Requirements</h2>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Investment Options</h3>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Option 1: National Development Fund (NDF) Donation</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Non-refundable contribution to the NDF supporting national development projects. The most popular
              choice for its simplicity—no property management or business involvement required.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Single applicant: $100,000</li>
              <li>• Family of up to 4: $100,000</li>
              <li>• Family of 5+: $125,000</li>
              <li>• Each additional dependent (after 5): $15,000</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Option 2: Real Estate Investment</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Purchase of approved real estate project. Property must be held for minimum 5 years. Joint ownership
              permitted (each buyer investing minimum $200,000).
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Minimum investment: $200,000 (approved projects only)</li>
              <li>• Holding period: 5 years minimum</li>
              <li>• Government fees apply separately</li>
              <li>• Property can generate rental income</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Option 3: Business Investment</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Investment in an approved business enterprise. Can be sole investment or joint venture with other
              CBI applicants (minimum $400,000 total, each applicant contributing at least $200,000).
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Single investor: $400,000 minimum</li>
              <li>• Joint investment: $200,000 per investor (minimum 2)</li>
              <li>• Must create at least 3 jobs</li>
              <li>• Government approval required</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Option 4: University of the West Indies Fund</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Contribution to UWI Fund providing one family member with a one-year scholarship (tuition only)
              at UWI campuses in Antigua, Barbados, Jamaica, or Trinidad.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Family of 6+: $150,000</li>
              <li>• Includes tuition scholarship for one family member</li>
              <li>• Good for families with university-age children</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Eligibility Criteria</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Age:</strong> Main applicant must be 18 years or older</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Clean record:</strong> No criminal convictions, no visa denials to countries with which Antigua has travel agreements</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Health:</strong> Good health status, health insurance required</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Source of funds:</strong> Legitimate and verifiable</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Dependents:</strong> Spouse, children under 30, parents/grandparents 55+, unmarried siblings under 18</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Required Documents</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">1.</span>
            <span>Completed application forms</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">2.</span>
            <span>Certified copy of passport (all pages)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">3.</span>
            <span>Birth certificate (certified and apostilled)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">4.</span>
            <span>Marriage certificate if applicable (certified and apostilled)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">5.</span>
            <span>Police clearance certificate from all countries of residence (past 10 years)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">6.</span>
            <span>Medical examination certificate</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">7.</span>
            <span>Proof of address (utility bill or bank statement)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">8.</span>
            <span>Professional reference letter</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">9.</span>
            <span>Bank reference letter</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">10.</span>
            <span>Source of funds documentation (6 months bank statements, employment/business records)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">11.</span>
            <span>8 passport-sized photos (per applicant)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">12.</span>
            <span>Health insurance certificate</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Insurance Requirements -->
    <section id="insurance-requirements" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Insurance Requirements</h2>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">Health Insurance is Mandatory</h3>
        <p class="text-amber-900">
          Antigua and Barbuda requires proof of health insurance as part of the CBI application. Coverage must be
          valid for Antigua and should include medical evacuation given the limited local healthcare facilities.
          While specific coverage minimums aren't mandated, comprehensive international health insurance is strongly
          recommended.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Minimum Recommendations</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Annual coverage: $500,000+ recommended</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Medical evacuation coverage (essential)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Coverage valid in Antigua and Barbuda</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Valid certificate for application submission</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Why Evacuation Coverage is Critical</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Only one public hospital (Mount St. John's)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Limited specialist care available locally</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Evacuation to Miami: 3.5 hours by air</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Air ambulance costs $20,000-$50,000+</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Insurance Strategy for CBI Applicants</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-900 mb-4">
          Most CBI applicants don't actually relocate to Antigua—they visit occasionally while maintaining residence
          elsewhere. Consider your actual situation:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-blue-900">
